data.description: A cozy place to call home in sought-after Keller ISD! Nestled in the quiet Park Glen neighborhood, at the corner of a cul-de-sac. This spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home features bright natural light, laminate wood floors, a gas fireplace, new interior paint and lighting, and google home switches in all rooms. All bedrooms are located on the second floor, with a game room. Perfect for entertaining, the front living room and dining room opens to the eat-in kitchen, which has granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and offers ample counter space. The windows across the back of the house provide an open view of the spacious backyard, from both the kitchen and rear living room. The front and back patios have been resurfaced. The longer driveway offers extra parking, so your guests do not have to park on the street. Contact us today to schedule a tour and see all this home has to offer!
